### /comment

This endpoint allows the user to post a comment in a discussion.

#### Request Body

- `discussionId` (string, required): The ID of the discussion where the comment is being posted.

- `text` (string, required): The content of the comment.


#### Response

The response is a JSON object with the following properties:

- `status` (boolean): Indicates the status of the request.

- `data` (object): Contains the details of the posted comment, including discussion ID, user ID, comment text, likes, ID, replies, creation timestamp, and last update timestamp.


#### JSON Schema

``` json
